## Radis {#radis}

Radis is a local currency used in the city of Geneva, Switzerland. It is equivalent to the national currency (1 Radis = 1 CHF). Radis is issued by Calim â€” The Geneva Food Bank ([calim-ge.ch](https://calim-ge.ch)).

To support Radis, contact Calim ([caisse@calim-ge.ch](mailto:caisse@calim-ge.ch)) to obtain the necessary parameters.

### Required Parameters

- **Unique account identifier**: identifier of your Radis.Calim account (integer)
- **Wallet address**: address of your wallet on the blockchain (string)
- **Secret key**: Decryption key, allowing to read the transaction reference number (string). Keep this key confidential.

> Payments in local currency are automatically imported by the system every night, securely.
